bgm.name: 007. ノリノリなシンキングタイム (saruyama)

parameters: The time of the visit to the listening session.
It's rare to see the department manager as the target.

Well, even though you can see it right away when you climb
the mountain,
Hahaha, wasn't it good to feel the sense of survival?
The confident department manager is confused by Kanae.
Should we take a picture for now?

Let's use it as a negotiation tactic when there is a
disadvantage later.
So, why didn't you talk to us?

It's like some kind of event, or rather, if you say
mystery, it's survival, and if you say survival, it's a
mystery, isn't it?
I thought I was fulfilling my club activities~

You just became someone who lives in poverty, right? You
were a homeless person with a roof over your head.
If you have a roof, you're not homeless...
I completely agree from the start.
Because of that, we completely blew away the summer event...

Since I got a lot this time, I'll pull the limited character
for this time.
It's not too late since it's until this week.
Kenta-senpai? My story isn't over yet.
Saruyama is still saying unproductive things.

This person seems to never change no matter what kind of
event they experience...
Um, Boss, then should I call my parents or...
I have conveyed everything properly, darling~.

The two of you seemed suspicious... and the girl followed
after you. But, she quickly...

So you're saying that you were going in and out of a
pachinko parlor?
No way! Tell me in advance!

The boss said they want to give everyone a surprise event
as a present...
By the way, aren't you angry?

It's true that it was anticlimactic, but I'm not angry. It
was somewhat interesting...
Try saying that to this big brother.
Are you going to hit me? Shall I hit you back?!
Hey, you're already hitting me, hey!
